text: Marija Ivandekić (born 25 August 1925) was a Yugoslav gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Yugoslav female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
